<%- include("partials/header") %>

<main class="container">

<section class="hero-upgrade">
  <img src="/images/hero-upgrade.jpg" alt="Upgrade your Boxed Mac and Cheese">  
  <h1>How to Upgrade Your Boxed Mac & Cheese 🧀</h1>
  <p>
    Boxed mac and cheese is already delicious, but with a few simple upgrades
    you can transform it into a gourmet comfort meal. From richer cheeses to
    creative toppings, these tricks will elevate any box of mac.
  </p>
</section>

<section class="upgrade-grid">

<div class="upgrade-card">
<img src="/images/upgrade-cheese.jpg" alt="Extra cheese mac">
<h2>Add Real Cheese</h2>
<p>
  Stir in freshly shredded cheeses like cheddar, gouda, or gruyère.
  The boxed cheese powder creates the base while real cheese adds
  depth and creaminess.
</p>
</div>

<div class="upgrade-card">
<img src="/images/upgrade-butter-cream.jpg" alt="Creamy mac and cheese">
<h2>Use Cream Instead of Milk</h2>
<p>
  Replace milk with heavy cream or half-and-half for an ultra rich,
  velvety sauce that coats every noodle.
</p>
</div>

<div class="upgrade-card">
<img src="/images/upgrade-protein.jpg" alt="Mac and cheese with bacon">
<h2>Add Protein</h2>
<p>
  Turn boxed mac into a full meal by adding bacon, grilled chicken,
  lobster, shrimp, or even diced ham.
</p>
</div>

<div class="upgrade-card">
<img src="/images/upgrade-crunch.jpg" alt="Crunchy mac topping">
<h2>Add a Crunchy Topping</h2>
<p>
  Sprinkle crushed crackers, panko breadcrumbs, or crushed Cheez-Its
  on top and broil for a crispy golden crust.
</p>
</div>

<div class="upgrade-card">
<img src="/images/upgrade-spice.jpg" alt="Spicy mac and cheese">
<h2>Boost the Flavor</h2>
<p>
  Add hot sauce, smoked paprika, garlic powder, or a dash of mustard
  to deepen the cheese flavor.
</p>
</div>

<div class="upgrade-card">
<img src="/images/upgrade-veggies.jpg" alt="Mac with broccoli">
<h2>Add Vegetables</h2>
<p>
  Broccoli, peas, spinach, roasted mushrooms, or caramelized onions
  add color, nutrition, and texture.
</p>
</div>

</section>


<section class="pro-tip">
<h2>Chef-Level Upgrade</h2>
<p>
Try mixing boxed mac with a homemade cheese sauce. The powdered cheese
provides bold flavor while the fresh sauce creates a silky texture.
This hybrid approach creates the ultimate comfort food.
</p>
</section>

</main>

